Title: Crossroads (2)
Plot: As Baltar's trial comes to a conclusion, key members of the fleet discover that they may be the Final Five Cylons. Tigh attempts to decipher the strange music he is hearing in his head, while a Cylon fleet approaches.
GuestStars: Nicki Clyne,  Mark A. Sheppard,  Chelah Horsdal,  Alessandro Juliani,  Susan Hogan,  Brad Dryborough,  William Samples,  Stephen Holmes, Keegan Connor Tracy,  Alison Matthews,  Jennifer Halley,  Donnelly Rhodes
